reviewText: IT WAS GOD TO SEE SOMETHING ABOUT THE WOMEN OF GOD. IT WAS TRULY INSPIRING AND GREAT MOVIE. THANKS AND SHALOM

There is little to this DVD.  There is no good explanation when you order it that there are only three stories.  Two of them are in Aramaic, so the audience cannot appreciate the DVD without reading.  I would not order from this series again.

Make sure if you are American , you get an English version, we watched it and we don't like sub titles and closed caption, so that's why we gave it a low rating, these are short stories, not a good buy for $7.00 + s/h
Ruth is not in the movie, movie was shorter than I would of liked, but not a bad movie, was ok
